{"tid":1508441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個再做大偵探捉鬼，我 立 即 屌 你 老 母！","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:12:00.000Z","uid":66260,"like":10,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f15b193309a4c91f961b0446c6be1c55f14c7b9","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再話前線某個人形跡可疑係鬼，你咁樣係侮辱緊所有前線既抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n唔好再將前線所有行為賴晒落警畜到，就算你係明知故屈，你呢種行為等同割席<br />\n<br />\n就算真係有鬼帶頭，我地要做既就係順住&ldquo;鬼&rdquo;既行為將抗爭升級：鬼掟一支雞尾酒，我地掟夠一百支<br />\n<br />\n811點解會俾內鬼反咬？係因為唔夠多人，只要夠多真手足企埋一齊，一個內鬼拉人後果就係俾五個手足圍毆<br />\n<br />\n喺未證實一個抗爭者係鬼之前，疑中留情，永不割席"},{"pid":"43439107881e2e3b668bc4dc1934b993a490c6e0","tid":1508441,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507880</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=200a2b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1GCRs7ie1gwrmV6-388fnE5PnFq_jnbwe</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAp4ft3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAp4ft3.jpg&h=2a9e5a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJK4ft3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJK4ft3.jpg&h=2ab03403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1GijVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1GijVJ.png&h=ecffc0d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15da5c42c53331c000e5fc2d62c3703dca76babc","tid":1508441,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e42e7bf1e871f803a1f0a413eb7bf2f97ab74f6","tid":1508441,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=0a7d9282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=637dc72e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=947d2aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"db88fc2463ffb4643a5914e82394b72f9a46cac2","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86adc60bc99c75c53b3fb578fe9adfa9dd7d803e","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"請勿將所有抗爭行為入晒警渣臥底數，因為這樣如同跟所有勇武者割席。<br />\n<br />\n如果有人說：「嘩！你D暴徒放火呀！」你可能會本能地辯護說：「係警察做架，屈示威者架。」好似很輕鬆就可反駁對方，但其實你也會同時自我暗示、否定了手足做那種事。此風一長，後果嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n因為警渣的武力正在不斷升級，而抗爭手段卻一直受道德潔癖所窘，去到一個地步，即使警渣已近距離射擊你的手足，你也不許他們還擲一枚汽油彈。然後，「請所有勇武立即停止」的呼聲就愈來愈響亮，大部分都關心手足的安危，有些則別有用心，但我不說下去了，免得被說成分化。我只想喚起大家的一個初衷：咩叫核彈都唔割？<br />\n<br />\n就係對抗暴政，任何行為皆可。<br />\n<br />\n咁殺人包唔包？<br />\n<br />\n如果你的核彈都唔割原來係唔包殺人，我唔知你個核彈係咩構造。<br />\n<br />\n距離香港人喪命還有多遠，我們不敢問，也不敢想像。當然，42樓班冚家剷恨不得有警察殉職，來個民意逆轉，我們都不想像他們那般黑心，但我好心你記得，已有六位義士獻上自己的生命，將光復香港的遺願托孤於你，而你如果只想早早散水，草草完結了這場血腥又骯髒的廝殺的話，就愧對了他們的寄盼，亦辜負了600位被捕義士的付出(不少被捕者連義士也不是)。<br />\n<br />\n運動一日未完，政治檢控就會被押後多一日，是以空間換取時間，直到暴政再也抵不住極限施壓為止。不過現在，為何抵不住施壓的那一方反是我們呢？<br />\n<br />\n好好運用你的憤怒和腦袋，鬥智也要鬥力，可以偃旗息鼓，萬不可鳴金收兵，因為大軍一退，就是他們掩殺的好時機。兵凶戰危，你可能一時失了方寸，但請你提醒自己，是怎樣一路走來，抗爭不斷，方可在極權手上營救手足呀！<br />\n<br />\n臥底們，即管借助你永不被捕的至高權力，代香港人盡情攻擊這個殘暴不仁的極權吧！<br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"2297ebb5689de5ecbe1c5c8b4b2a7179eb215a75","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/26/223030_b3943f8f804a45333bea6869f1d7d410.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F223030_b3943f8f804a45333bea6869f1d7d410.png&h=0b006ad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d823d5b29107e7b4d03de6adc42c07dc1530b140","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbf33b1b1938dc3ec8ec69b752fc55aa063d4db","tid":1508441,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"你地明唔明所謂對抗暴政，任何行為皆可係唔會令我地贏？"},{"pid":"4c7248dfb3ca21e507e363c379696702c7e37e31","tid":1508441,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"咩事都要講事實既 唔好再係到帶風向啦樓主"},{"pid":"47aa03a55561093dd9af904c9b5b7d4eb069aad0","tid":1508441,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7248dfb3ca21e507e363c379696702c7e37e31","tid":1508441,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,